snippet.title: Pillow Talk TV
snippet.description:
Comedy with attitude. Sex comedy, marijuana comedy, and weird funny series for stoners and narks alike. Over 300 episodes of dirty, sexy, weird, funny, wild, quirky sex comedy. Some think we've crossed the line on Pillow Talk TV, but isn't that the point? All great comedy makes you uncomfortable. Why stop there? This is your new favorite channel!

Mandi Mellen and Dan Salem have two big channels and one big... comedy. Pillow Talk TV will make you hot. They make you laugh as actors, writers and directors.  Videos on Friday, straight out of Los Angeles. @PillowTalk_TV on IG and @LetsPillowTalk on FB and Twitter.

Our other big channel is BuzzChomp Entertainment: @BuzzChomp on Youtube and @BuzzzChomp on FB and Twitter. 

Pillow Talk TV is sponsored by @The Healthy_LA (on IG) mainstream cannabis brand (www.TheHealthyLA.com) and part of www.BuzzChomp.com your home for Fitness Entertainment!
Contact us to contribute!
